file_content.text: Impressive. Truly impressive.
Keep at it! Almost got him!
I fear there's no room left for hope.
Oh, no.
His anger fuels him.
Press the attack!
Obliterate him.
Trouble up ahead. I don't know if the Revanites have been experimenting or what, but they've got their hands on the mother of all Massassi.
A terrifying specimen. I don't envy you right now.
I have every faith in you, but you must hurry!
Destroy him!
Take him down!
Come on, I know you got this!
You've only served to make him more irate, I'm afraid.
Focus!
Congratulations. You officially ticked him off.

Yeah, I hear you. Bad news....
Better get moving. Guarantee you Revan isn't taking his sweet time in there.
